1. Ja sam *poznavala* tu osobu pre nego što se preselila u drugi grad. (I used to know that person before she moved to another city.)
2. Ona je *poznavala* svog dedu vrlo dobro, ali nikada ga nije upoznala lično. (She knew her grandpa very well, but she never met him in person.)
3. Kada sam *poznavala* Marka, bio je mnogo drugačiji nego sada. (When I knew Mark, he was very different from now.)
4. Moja majka me je *poznavala* bolje nego bilo ko drugi. (My mother knew me better than anyone else.)
5. Pre nego što smo se venčali, nismo se *poznavali* dovoljno dugo. (Before we got married, we didn't know each other long enough.)
6. *Poznavala* sam da je ovo bio poslednji put da ćemo se videti. (I knew that this was the last time we would see each other.)
7. Da li si *poznavala* da je to bila njena omiljena pesma? (Did you know that was her favorite song?)
8. Kada smo se *poznavali*, nikada nismo razgovarali o politici. (When we knew each other, we never talked about politics.)
9. Ona je *poznavala* istoriju svog rodnog grada veoma dobro. (She knew the history of her hometown very well.)
10. Da li si *poznavala* da je ovo jedan od najboljih restorana u gradu? (Did you know that this is one of the best restaurants in town?)